Mr. Parikh i/by. Mahimtura and Co. for the defendants. P.C. : P.C. : P.C. : . Mentioned. Not on Board. 1. By consent of the parties the following order is passed : :2: 2. The matter to continue before the Commissioner and the Commissioner will take all the documents on record subject to objection which will be determined at the hearing of the suit. The Commissioner is directed to conduct and complete the evidence of the remaining witness on record and record the objections which are raised by the parties. The same will be determined at the hearing of the suit. 3. The Commissioner is empowered to close the evidence of the witness who is not co-operating inspite of giving two adjournments. The Commissioner is directed to complete the evidence on or before 31.5.2006 and file report by 10.6.2006. *********
